data.description: Experience the epitome of luxury living in Palm Springs at this exceptional home located in the prestigious Escena community. This residence showcases a detached casita and highlights the upgraded bifold doors, as well as the owned solar panels. Relax and unwind in the private backyard, complete with a sparkling pool/spa. Inside, be immersed in modern living with an open floorplan, vaulted ceilings, and abundant natural light streaming through clerestory windows. The bifold doors seamlessly merge indoor and outdoor spaces, creating an unparalleled indoor/outdoor living experience. With 3 bedrooms and 3 baths, this home offers ample space and comfort for you and your loved ones. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring a large island with a quartz countertop, a walk-in pantry, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, including double ovens. The luxurious primary suite boasts double vanities, a soothing soaking tub, a walk-in closet, and direct patio access. Additionally, the detached casita with its own private entrance provides flexibility and convenience. Not only is this home elegant, but it also prioritizes environmental consciousness with its solar panels, helping to reduce your carbon footprint. Motorized shades in the living room add a touch of sophistication, while the attached 2-car garage ensures utmost convenience. Escena offers a gated community with coveted amenities, including a bark park and low HOA fees.
